opportunities in the new century," the official said. "We hope it
will be a new century of peace, stability and common prosperity."
</P>
<P>
"To realize the aspiration, we have no other option but to
strengthen cooperation among all countries and nations on the
basis of mutual respect, equality and mutual benefit," he said.
</P>
<P>
"China is ready to make its contribution to the realization of
this goal," Li said, noting a more effective way to use resources
on earth is needed to "better protect this shared home of ours."
