<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, February 1 (Xinhua) -- Lesotho Prime Minister
Ntsu Mokhehle has asked to be relieved of the ruling Lesotho
Congress for Democracy (LCD)'s leadership.
</P>
